"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Recently I've written a lot about web3 use cases, from [organising raves as DAOs](https://www.musicxtechxfuture.com/2021/06/08/the-community-owned-rave-event-organisers-as-daos/), to [1,000 true fan organisations](https://www.musicxtechxfuture.com/2021/06/01/the-decentralized-autonomous-1000-true-fan-organisation/), to the [basics of bootstrapping a DAO](https://www.musicxtechxfuture.com/2021/06/22/blockchain-basics-how-to-start-a-dao/). \\n\\nIn order to get more of you actively participating, this post goes into something more practical: setting up a wallet & acquiring an NFT. I've set it up as a video:\\n\\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p0OByzktIaA\\n\\nA step-by-step guide on:\\n* How to set up a cryptowallet using **Metamask**\\n* Adding cryptocurrency to your wallet using **Coinbase**\\n* Buying your first NFT on **ENS**\\n* Monitoring transactions on **Etherscan**\\n* Giving your wallet a nice address like basgras.eth or musicxblockchain.eth\\n\\nLinks:\\nhttps://metamask.io/\\nhttps://www.coinbase.com/\\nhttps://ens.domains/\\n\\nI spent about $50 on gas fees and .eth addresses in order to create this video. This is why I have a [Patreon community for MUSIC x](https://patreon.com/musicx) whose contributions help me cover the costs associated with running the sites & newsletter. Thank you! ðŸ–¤\\n\\nIf you want to put your new wallet to use and would like a more Web3 method to contribute, you can send a tip to this smart contract, which will then automatically split your tip to the musicxblockchain.eth and basgras.eth wallets. ETH in the former wallet will be used to fund future projects.\\n\\n[MUSIC x Blockchain](split://0x31F5242b4BaEA2e1AEeC0e8181C66C5B224eE96c?network=mainnet)\\n\\n-\\n***MUSIC x is a regular [newsletter](http://musicx.email/) about innovation in music, subscribed to by thousands of people in music, entertainment & tech.**\\nFollow us on Twitter [@musicxnetwork](https://twitter.com/musicxnetwork).*\\n\",\"timestamp\":1625550860,\"title\":\"Web3 primer: setting up your cryptowallet & buying your first NFT\",\"publication\":\"musicx\"},\"digest\":\"BBnUjHOfIWXSsVUVoXWDAfJqxvibSL43hmLnTFhH3dk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe612d9C2a9bA0Ff4403F4f7Ea87D5bE4290aC7B9\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"9w6CW2uF3aRESNeJuI4AANb1eqfqfq9IewZTY3FiyD8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"9u7E8n6eAaaWNdePKt6GoX3CwmqXO2cAZpzGz2YKg9g\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"m8EUW69K2dAjjyFT8oemX0C62plLPlWM4G4ZLsIP6lTphjy-tpYD8d6gtlh1CP4wewUQ96lDd2FxZodL60d3wQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xa80aeb5f299633d3edfe6d065d03091f24038cf097a5c6ce6e82cc216f4432014670c029322e5c1f2615be5386378ce17d005b8323ee2a9211fa8fbbe75501491b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on musicx.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"9w6CW2uF3aRESNeJuI4AANb1eqfqfq9IewZTY3FiyD8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"9u7E8n6eAaaWNdePKt6GoX3CwmqXO2cAZpzGz2YKg9g\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"aFsodqVCC0JTCQ48z002Gecdkq0w9-2tGa-YqXp3BB0\"}"